			<div class="content" id="post-content-4260931">
									

<h3><span>What’s up my finna lit squadfam? How’s it chillaxing? Enjoy that fire tale? Why not check out my other totally radical stuff, bruh?</span></h3>
<h1><span><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/henzoids-author-page" target="_blank">Yeet</a></span></h1>
<hr />
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596039879" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span> for helping work out a few issues with the first draft of this.</p>
<p>Thanks so much to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596039879" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596039879" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3487700); return false;">Uncle Nicolini</a></span> for helping to improve the piece after its initial posting. Without them, it would certainly have never made it past +20, much less +50.</p>
<hr />
<p>To those who are coming from Demasqed, this is a tale I wrote a while ago and incorporated into Demasqed. To those who aren't coming from Demasqed, add <tt>/offset/1</tt> to the end of the tale's url to see what I'm talking about.</p>
<hr />
<p><a href="https://search.creativecommons.org/photos/6fdbdc4e-73c4-4283-9776-3ab6709d2f1a" target="_blank">Epic Image Credits</a></p>

